### 7. **WASM Integration**

**File:** `/Users/mike/github/sw-embed/cor24-rs/src/wasm.rs` (lines 1-293)

The `WasmCpu` struct provides JS-accessible methods:
- `assemble(source: &str)` - assembles code and loads into memory
- `step()` - execute one instruction
- `run_batch(max_instructions)` - execute batch with animation
- `run()` - run until halt
- `get_registers()` - return all 8 registers
- `get_memory_slice(start, len)` - read memory range
- `get_leds()`, `set_switches()`, `uart_send_char()` - I/O control
- `get_uart_output()` - read UART TX buffer
- `get_trace_lines(n)` - last N instruction trace entries
- `get_sparse_sram()`, `get_sparse_ebr()` - memory for display

